ications (that we use to collect candidates\' information) and convert them into HTML forms that submit data to our database OR use google forms API to capture google form details and insert them into our database. In both case, retain all basic information and a score obtained by the person</li>\n<li>once the application is stored in the database, send a confirmation email to the applicant about the submission status</li>\n<li>add an evaluation page where the admin can check the applicant profile and confirm if the applicant will proceed in the next stage or not. in all two cases, send an email notification</li>\n<li>As a role of thumb, all applicants accepted will be supposed to fill another form where they will download the NDA template, fill it and upload it back to the system</li>\n<li>once NDA has been uploaded, the system will automatically register that user into the authentication table and send an email of username and password letting the person proceed for X days with training in academy.shulesoft.com and in demo.shulesoft.com</li>\n<li>After x days, the system will send automatically a link to the applicant to fill the online quiz which will weigh if the person reaches a particular mark or not. if a person reaches a required mark, the system will automatically book a meeting with the person and send a link for an online interview to the applicant and to ShuleSoft management&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Once the interview is done, the system should show an option for management to put a mark on the interviewed person and confirm if the person will work with us or not by specifying salary basic payment as well</li>\n<li>once management approved, the system will send a confirmation email of employment to the employee and include all obligations (procedures) for an employee to follow in order to join the company. These obligations will also include a link for the employee to submit a signed contract file, other academic particulars, and passport size</li>\n<li>once the 